import { Component } from '@angular/core'; import { CommonModule } from '@angular/common'; import { ActivatedRoute } from '@angular/router'; import { QuoteService } from '../../services/quote.service'; import { Quote } from '../../models'; @Component({ standalone: true, selector: 'app-public', imports: [CommonModule], templateUrl: './public.component.html', styleUrls: ['./public.component.css'] }) export class PublicComponent { quote: Quote | null = null; constructor(private route: ActivatedRoute, private svc: QuoteService) { const slug = this.route.snapshot.paramMap.get('slug')!; this.quote = this.svc.getBySlug(slug); } }
